articles.title: Sex toy tossed on court during WNBA game in L.A., latest of several such incidents - CBS News
articles.description: A sex toy landed near Indiana's Sophie Cunningham after it was thrown from the stands in L.A. while the Fever played the Sparks in the latest of several such  incidents.
articles.content:
